data.description: Come and see this elegant 3BR, 2.5BA plus Bonus Room and Sun room home in a quiet Simpsonville community! Conveniently located near Fairview Rd shopping, I385 and Downtown Simpsonville! You will find that this home has space for the whole family and comes with many big ticket updates, including: an architectural shingled roof, premium heavy duty gutters and downspouts, HVAC upstairs and downstairs, tankless gas hot water heater, new luxury vinyl flooring downstairs, and all new carpet upstairs. New black hardware trim and modern lighting throughout. No popcorn ceilings here and home is freshly painted throughout with a neutral white color. Home features a true Great Room that measures 25x15 with a wood burning fireplace, a spacious 17x12 dining room for the family table, in addition to a 12x11 breakfast room that rivals many dining rooms, a charming sunroom off the back of the great room and a capacious 21x19 bonus room upstairs with all kinds of potential!  The oversized garage has a 9x6 framed workshop area with a storage loft above. Back yard is ready for family activities and includes a custom built fire pit, inground trampoline and zip line. Back yard is fenced for security and the trees afford some shade in the summer months. Have peace of mind with the solid construction of the mid 90's and being in a established community. Enjoy a driveway that 4 vehicles can comfortably park in! New price just reduced by $14,000 - Now only $335,000!
